install_msg:
Thanks for install.
Don't forget to set api key (`[p]forecastapi`)
If you don't have registered DarkSky API key, this cog will be useless to you.
DarkSky API closing at end of 2021 and im aware of this.
description: Weather forecast. Requires "semi-private" DarkSky API key. For more info: https://rapidapi.com/darkskyapis/api/dark-sky
end_user_data_statement: This cog may does not persistently store any PII data or metadata about users.
